    <h1>API (Application Programming Interface)</h1>
    <p class="description">The rules and protocols that let one software application request data or actions from another. APIs are the connective tissue of the modern martech stack — <strong>over 83% of internet traffic</strong> is now API calls according to Akamai.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
